The paper deals with the problem of belief tracking in planning with sensing, which is a core problem in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and planning (cs.PL). The paper also introduces a new algorithm and approximation technique, which involve machine learning and optimization techniques (cs.LG) and robotics (cs.RO) as well as control systems (cs.SY).
